This is my first blog post ... it is on AWS autoscaling in production ... I will write a series of posts on managing AWS, review of different data stores, redis or memcached for caching and different use cases for redis, different methods for automating deployments, scalable logging solutions, managing elasticsearch and a review of using it as a primary data store with a case study, common vulnerabilities and how to secure them, recover from an attack and do basic forensic analysis ... etc
Feedback is highly appreciated
